Localization.Name: Roussimoff Rehabilitation Systems
Localization.Description: Roussimoff Rehabilitation Systems (RRS) is an Earth-based corporation that provides rehabilitation services, personal body armor and defensive systems throughout the UEE. Their arms division is responsible for a groundbreaking series of new weaponry designed to incapacitate opponents without taking lives.

Localization.Name: Morozov-SH Legs Snowdrift
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Heavy Armor
Damage Reduction: 40%
Temp. Rating: -90 / 115 °C
Radiation Protection: 26800 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 145.8 REM/s
Carrying Capacity: 7.5K µSCU

Featuring fortified armor plating, special anti-rip protective padding and ample storage, the Morozov-SH is ready to overcome all kinds of adversity. After consulting with security professionals, RRS added a unique high protective collar and a lightweight inner lining based on their recommendation; making the Morozov-SH both comfortable and a battlefield stalwart.

Localization.Name: Virgil
Localization.Description:
High-end Commercial and Personal armor manufacturer. Aside from combat uses, they build systems for heavy commercial and mining applications.

Models: Achilles PDS (Heavy Combat Armor)

Zeus System (Titan Armor)

Localization.Name: ForceFlex Undersuit Black/Red
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Undersuit
Damage Reduction: 10%
Temp. Rating: -30 / 60 °C
Radiation Protection: 15200 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 81 REM/s
Carrying Capacity: 8.0 µSCU

Virgil's ForceFlex is the next generation in undersuit technology. Rated for combat as well as industrial work, you can rest assured that the comboweave will keep you protected in whatever situation you put it through.
